Revision history for Data-CountingBloomFilter-Shared

0.01      2026-07-09
          - Initial release. Shared-memory counting Bloom filter: approximate
            set membership with delete (remove) and per-item occurrence counts
            (count_of), on 4-bit saturating counters. XXH3-128 double hashing;
            backed by a file, an anonymous mapping, or a memfd; write-preferring
            futex rwlock with dead-process recovery. Counter-wise saturating
            merge. Linux, 64-bit Perl.
